    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-63708140.pdf_170_2",
    "text": "7)灯光照明系统",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.15397881676025837,
      0.4954091067694028,
      0.31822288797120063,
      0.5142956709570926
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-63708140.pdf_170",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-63708140.pdf_170_3",
    "text": "整车碰撞试验过程中，由于摄像帧数一般要求为1000，常规灯光根本无法满足 碰撞拍摄要求。因此，在碰撞区需要设置专用的灯光照明系统。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11086474806738603,
      0.5302766098851379,
      0.8889710354292251,
      0.5724081761499845
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-63708140.pdf_170",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-63708140.pdf_170_4",
    "text": "照明系统平均照度应不小于100000lx，具有B0OST（推进)功能，即光源的控制 可以提供50%，100%，200%的光源输出，可通过控制软件点击启动，也可由外部信号 触发启动。照明区域要能覆盖整个碰撞区域，并且灯架能在三轴向进行移动。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11086474806738603,
      0.5767666140394514,
      0.8889710354292251,
      0.643595995011277
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-63708140.pdf_170",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-63708140.pdf_170_5",
    "text": "灯光系统能与整车牵引控制系统配合工作，完成完整的碰撞试验（见图3.72)。 灯光系统在接收牵引系统给予的外部触发信号后，能实现灯光的推进(Boost)功能； 同时，灯光系统也能将自己系统的相关工作状态信息反馈给牵引控制系统，便于试 验人员对灯光系统的工作状态进行监控。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.10881169717724926,
      0.6479544329007438,
      0.8889710354292251,
      0.7380288159497261
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-63708140.pdf_170",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-63708140.pdf_170_6",
    "text": "目前，主流的灯光照明系统制造商有Atlas（美国）、Visol（韩国）、Messring（德 国）。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1047055953969757,
      0.7409344412093708,
      0.8930771372094986,
      0.7845188201040396
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-63708140.pdf_170",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-63708140.pdf_170_7",
    "text": "8)假人及标定系统",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.1519257658701216,
      0.7990469464022626,
      0.33875339687256845,
      0.8193863232197747
    ],
